<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Maximize Your Reach on YourApp</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo { max-width: 150px; }
    h1 { color: #4a4a4a; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .tips { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .stats { text-align: center; margin: 25px 0; }
    .stat-number { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #e74c3c; display: block; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="{{appUrl}}/images/creator-logo.png" alt="YourApp Creator Program" class="logo">
  </div>

  <h1>Ready to grow your audience, {{firstName}}?</h1>
  
  <p>It's been {{daysSinceSignup}} days since you joined our Creator Program, and we're excited to see you get started! Creators who publish within their first week typically see 3x more engagement.</p>
  
  <div class="stats">
    <span class="stat-number">3X</span>
    <span>more engagement for early creators</span>
  </div>
  
  <p>Here are some tips from our top creators to help you maximize your reach:</p>
  
  <div class="tips">
    <h3>Creator Success Tips:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Post Consistently</strong>: Regular content keeps your audience engaged</li>
      <li><strong>Analyze Performance</strong>: Use your analytics to see what resonates</li>
      <li><strong>Engage With Comments</strong>: Build community by responding quickly</li>
      <li><strong>Cross-Promote</strong>: Share your YourApp content on other platforms</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{createUrl}}" class="button">Create New Content</a>
  </div>
  
  <p>Remember to check your <a href="{{analyticsUrl}}">Creator Analytics</a> regularly to track your growth and understand your audience better.</p>
  
  <p>Need inspiration or have questions? Our Creator Support team is here to help you succeed!</p>
  
  <p>Creating success together,<br>The YourApp Creator Team</p>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} YourApp. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>123 App Street, San Francisco, CA 94107</p>
    <p><small>You're receiving this email because you joined the YourApp Creator Program. If you no longer wish to receive these emails, <a href="{{appUrl}}/creator/email-preferences?email={{email}}">update your preferences</a>.</small></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>